    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a compliance document classifier. Based on the document summary and key terms, assign the most relevant categories.\n\nDOCUMENT INFO:\nTitle: {{ $json.title }}\nSummary: {{ $json.summary }}\nKey Terms: {{ $json.key_terms }}\n\nAssign categories:\n\n**Main Topics** (select 3-5 most relevant):\n- Jurisdictions: Federal, EPA, Alabama, Florida, Georgia, Mississippi, North Carolina, South Carolina, Tennessee\n- Resources: Water Quality, Stormwater, Wetlands, Riparian Buffers, Air Quality, Soil Conservation, Waste Management, Wildlife, Forestry, Agriculture, Coastal\n- Programs: NPDES, Section 404, Section 401, Section 10, CWA, NEPA, ESA, Mining Permits, Air Permits\n- Activities: Construction, Permits, Development, Dredge and Fill, Agriculture, Forestry, Mining, Stormwater Management\n- Doc Types: Regulation, Guidance, Court Decision, Proposed Rule, Final Rule, Permit, Fact Sheet\n\n**Geographic Scope** (select 1-5 that apply):\n- National\n- Regional (e.g., Southeast, Coastal States)\n- State-specific: Alabama, Florida, Georgia, Mississippi, North Carolina, South Carolina, Tennessee\n- Multi-State\n- Local\n\nExamples:\n- Federal regulation: [\"National\"]\n- Georgia state law: [\"Georgia\"]\n- EPA rule affecting Southeast: [\"National\", \"Regional\"]\n- Multi-state compact: [\"Georgia\", \"Alabama\", \"Tennessee\"]\n\n**IMPORTANT FORMAT RULE**: \nWhen selecting topics from the taxonomy categories above (Jurisdictions, Resources, Programs, Activities, Doc Types), return ONLY the value itself, NOT the category label.\n\nExample output:\n{\n  \"main_topics\": [\"Federal\", \"Water Quality\", \"NPDES\", \"Proposed Rule\"],\n  \"geographic_scope\": [\"National\"]\n}\n\nOUTPUT (valid JSON only, no other text):\n{\n  \"main_topics\": [\"topic1\", \"topic2\", \"topic3\"],\n  \"geographic_scope\": [\"scope1\", \"scope2\"]\n}\n",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [
        2384,
        0
      ],
      "id": "93c76ddf-eda8-4bd0-919b-5dc5b1a8b21a",
      "name": "AI Agent X2 - Topics"
